STATE
v.
Raymond Dakim Harris JOINER. No. 514P13-4. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 17, 2016. Raymond Joiner, Windsor, for Joiner, Raymond Dakim Harris. Ryan Frank Haigh, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of N.C. James R. O'Neill, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 1st of February 2016 by Defendant for Order for Dismissal:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th of March 2016."
